cu.explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to a negative value will cause an invalid configuration as the cell ID must be a non-negative integer.

du.explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to a negative value will cause an invalid configuration as the cell ID must be a non-negative integer.
du.explanation_zh: 將 nr_cellid 設定為負值會導致無效配置，因為細胞 ID 必須為非負整數。
